2026-05-10T18:05:08.9142141Z 240            cannot restore it from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-10T18:05:08.9142460Z 241            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-10T18:05:08.9142816Z 242            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-10T18:05:08.9143048Z 243            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-10T18:05:08.9143436Z 244            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-10T18:05:08.9143765Z 245            ensures the activity is finished as soon as it leaves the
2026-05-10T18:05:08.9144116Z 246            foreground and is never re-entered with a missing extra. See
2026-05-10T18:05:08.9144461Z 247            crash report tagged "ProxyBillingActivity NPE" for context.
